			<div id="post-544" class="post-544 post type-post hentry category-uncategorized">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://colbertrally.com/cbs-estimated-215000-rally-attendees/544" title="Permalink to CBS estimated 215,000 rally attendees" rel="bookmark">CBS estimated 215,000 rally attendees</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://colbertrally.com/cbs-estimated-215000-rally-attendees/544" title="8:26 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">October 30, 2010</span></a> <span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://colbertrally.com/author/admin/" title="View all posts by admin">admin</a></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<p><img src="http://www.colbertrally.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/stewart-colbert-rally.jpg" alt="" title="stewart-colbert-rally" width="620" height="350" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-545" /></p>
<p><a href="http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-503544_162-20021284-503544.html">CBS just reported</a> that 215,000 people attended the Rally to Restore Sanity and/or Fear. They contracted AirPhotosLive to make the aerial estimate.</p>
<p>Metro officials also confirmed that normally the metro serves about 180,000 people, but today they had about 400,000 users.</p>
<p>That&#8217;s pretty good for less than 2 months of promotion right?</p>
