			<div id="post-503" class="post-503 post type-post hentry category-uncategorized">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://colbertrally.com/creative-ways-to-keep-fear-alive/503" title="Permalink to Creative ways to Keep Fear Alive" rel="bookmark">Creative ways to Keep Fear Alive</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://colbertrally.com/creative-ways-to-keep-fear-alive/503" title="10:50 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">October 27, 2010</span></a> <span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://colbertrally.com/author/admin/" title="View all posts by admin">admin</a></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<p>The guys and gals at <a href="http://www.letterbombing.com">letterbombing.com</a> <em>(wow, now that&#8217;s just asking for the<a href="http://www.reddit.com/r/reddit.com/comments/dmh5s/does_this_mean_the_fbi_is_after_us/"> FBI to bug your car</a>)</em> just sent us this video of their handy work:</p>
<p><object width="640" height="385"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/fW9v7gr1nE4?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US&amp;hd=1"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/fW9v7gr1nE4?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US&amp;hd=1" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="640" height="385"></embed></object></p>
<p>While we <strong>DO NOT</strong> condone any type of vandalism or name calling, we do appreciate the creative things people do to support the Colbert Rally.</p>
<p>That being said, we want to actively encourage you, patriots of fear, to find creative ways to get more people to donate to <a href="http://www.donorschoose.org/truthiness">DonorsChoose.org/truthiness</a>.</p>
<p>So how about it? What creative idea or flashmob stunt do you have to help us reach our goal of $500,000. We are so-so close!</p>
